era Pavé 14K WG</a></td><td>$1,515</td><td><strong>from $4,715</strong></td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-search?shape=cushion&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">IGI 4ct F-VS1 Lab Cushion (L/W 1.15–1.25)</a></td><td>from $5,000</td><td><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/classic-four-prong-solitaire-engagement-ring-item-194156?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">Classic Four Prong Solitaire Platinum</a></td><td>$1,180</td><td><strong>from $6,180</strong></td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-search?shape=cushion&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">GIA 2ct F-VS1 Natural Cushion (L/W 1.15+)</a></td><td>from $9,800</td><td><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/classic-four-prong-solitaire-engagement-ring-item-194156?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">Classic Four Prong Solitaire Platinum</a></td><td>$1,180</td><td><strong>from $10,980</strong></td></tr></tbody></table>

